{"section": "3.8.4: Proving an inequality by induction.", "qid": 1, "instructions": "<div class=\"activity-instructions\">\n <p>\n  Consider a proof of the following fact:\n </p>\n <div style=\"float: left;\">\n  <div class=\"zyblock\">\n   For all\n   <span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">\n    n \u2265 4\n   </span>\n   ,\n   <span style=\"white-space: nowrap;\">\n    2\n    <sup>\n     n\n    </sup>\n    \u2265 n\n    <sup>\n     2\n    </sup>\n   </span>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div style=\"display: block; height: 0px; clear: both;\">\n </div>\n</div>\n", "question": "<div class=\"question\">\n <div class=\"setup flex-row\">\n  <div class=\"label\">\n   2)\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"text\">\n   What should be proven in the inductive step?\n  </div>\n </div>\n <fieldset>\n  <div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember205\" style=\"\">\n   <input aria-label=\"For n = 4, 2n \u2265 n2\" name=\"42\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember204&gt;\"/>\n   <label aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"\">\n    For n = 4, 2\n    <sup>\n     n\n    </sup>\n    \u2265 n\n    <sup>\n     2\n    </sup>\n   </label>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember207\" style=\"\">\n   <input aria-label=\"2k \u2265  k2\" name=\"42\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember206&gt;\"/>\n   <label aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"\">\n    2\n    <sup>\n     k\n    </sup>\n    \u2265  k\n    <sup>\n     2\n    </sup>\n   </label>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember209\" style=\"\">\n   <input aria-label=\"For every k \u2265 4,\n if 2k \u2265 k2,\n then 2k+1 \u2265 (k+1)2\" name=\"42\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember208&gt;\"/>\n   <label aria-hidden=\"true\" style=\"\">\n    For every k \u2265 4,\n    <br/>\n    if 2\n    <sup>\n     k\n    </sup>\n    \u2265 k\n    <sup>\n     2\n    </sup>\n    ,\n    <br/>\n    then 2\n    <sup>\n     k+1\n    </sup>\n    \u2265 (k+1)\n    <sup>\n     2\n    </sup>\n   </label>\n  </div>\n </fieldset>\n</div>\n", "choices": ["<div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember205\">\n <input aria-label=\"For n = 4, 2n \u2265 n2\" name=\"42\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember204&gt;\"/>\n <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  For n = 4, 2\n  <sup>\n   n\n  </sup>\n  \u2265 n\n  <sup>\n   2\n  </sup>\n </label>\n</div>\n", "<div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember207\">\n <input aria-label=\"2k \u2265  k2\" name=\"42\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember206&gt;\"/>\n <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  2\n  <sup>\n   k\n  </sup>\n  \u2265  k\n  <sup>\n   2\n  </sup>\n </label>\n</div>\n", "<div class=\"zb-radio-button orange orange ember-view\" id=\"ember209\">\n <input aria-label=\"For every k \u2265 4,\n if 2k \u2265 k2,\n then 2k+1 \u2265 (k+1)2\" name=\"42\" type=\"radio\" value=\"&lt;(unknown):ember208&gt;\"/>\n <label aria-hidden=\"true\">\n  For every k \u2265 4,\n  <br/>\n  if 2\n  <sup>\n   k\n  </sup>\n  \u2265 k\n  <sup>\n   2\n  </sup>\n  ,\n  <br/>\n  then 2\n  <sup>\n   k+1\n  </sup>\n  \u2265 (k+1)\n  <sup>\n   2\n  </sup>\n </label>\n</div>\n"], "answer": "For every k \u2265 4,\n if 2k \u2265 k2,\n then 2k+1 \u2265 (k+1)2", "explanation": "<div aria-atomic=\"true\" class=\"explanation has-explanation correct\" role=\"alert\">\n <p class=\"message\">\n  Correct\n </p>\n The inductive step assumes the statement is true for k and proves the statement for k+1.\n</div>\n"}